ErP A-rated for its high levels of efficiency, this robust and reliable regular boiler offers full compatibility with sustainable sources such as Bosch's Greenskies solar panels and Greensource air-to-water pumps, helping to improve the Danesmoor's eco-friendly credentials even further while also significantly reducing household costs.
